Libvirt-php is basically just PHP binding for libvirt virtualization toolkit.

Libvirt provides a portable, long term stable C API for managing the
virtualization technologies provided by many operating systems. It includes
support for QEMU, KVM, Xen, LXC, bhyve, Virtuozzo, VMware vCenter and ESX,
VMware Desktop, Hyper-V, VirtualBox and the POWER Hypervisor.

WWW: https://libvirt.org/php/
